'''Mukakamanzi Beatha''' numukinnyi wa filimi mu  [[Rwanda]] .  Umwe mu bakinnyi ba filime bazwi cyane mu [[Rwanda]], Beatha azwi cyane ku ruhare rwe nka 'Rosine', naho muri ''Giramata'' nka 'nyina wa Giramata'. 

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavukiye mu [[Akarere ka Gatsibo|Karere ka Gatsibo]] .

== Umwuga ==
Filime ye ya mbere yakinnye yaje muri firime ''The Deadly Spear.'' Nyuma ya firime, yakinnye muri firime nyinshi zizwi nka ''Rwasibo'', ''Intare yinngore'', ''Giramata n'inzindi'' , ''It's Not the End'', ''Dreams'', ''Enemy of Love'', ''Conclusion'', and ''Make Milk''..  Hanyuma yinjiye muri serivise izwi cyane ya ''City Maid'' . 

